HEADWORD: Nagana
<hw>Na*ga"na</hw> <pr>(n⟦adot⟧*g⟦aum⟧"n⟦adot⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Prob. native name.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A disease of
